%^BOLD%^-=%^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^Illusion Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Casters with access to this domain have the powerful force of perception on their side. They are able to protect themselves in various ways by throwing off those who try to see them, and they are likewise able to bring forth figments to torment others.

The illusion domain contains the following spells:

Blurred Movement, Invisibility, Displacement, Greater Invisibility, Phantasmal Killer, Screen, Shadow Double, Scintilating Pattern, Weird

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: The Faceless One

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
